column16: Dustin Pedroia hits a ground-rule double (14) on a fly ball down the right-field line.   Andrew Benintendi scores.
Andrew Benintendi doubles (12) on a line drive to left fielder Steve Pearce.   Mookie Betts scores.
Mookie Betts singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Kevin Pillar.   Christian Vazquez scores.    Deven Marrero scores.
Deven Marrero hits a ground-rule double (7) on a fly ball to right field.   Hanley Ramirez scores.    Jackie Bradley scores.    Christian Vazquez to 3rd.
Christian Vazquez singles on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Hanley Ramirez to 3rd.    Jackie Bradley to 2nd.
Jackie Bradley singles on a soft ground ball to shortstop Troy Tulowitzki.   Hanley Ramirez to 2nd.
Hanley Ramirez singles on a fly ball to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Dustin Pedroia grounds into a double play, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to second baseman Ryan Goins to first baseman Justin Smoak.   Andrew Benintendi out at 2nd.
Mookie Betts singles on a pop up to second baseman Ryan Goins.   Deven Marrero to 3rd.
Deven Marrero singles on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Jackie Bradley scores.    Xander Bogaerts scores.    Deven Marrero to 2nd on the throw.
